        "## 1. Entropy as a Controlled State Variable\n",
        "\n",
        "$$H(I) = -\\sum_i p_i \\log p_i$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Entropy is treated as a **first-class system state**, not a diagnostic metric.\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\\frac{dH}{d\\theta} = -\\sum_i \\frac{dp_i}{d\\theta}(\\log p_i + 1)$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Control Law**\n",
        "$$|\\nabla_\\theta H| \\le \\epsilon \\Rightarrow \\text{Autonomous inference}$$\n",
        "$$|\\nabla_\\theta H| > \\epsilon \\Rightarrow \\text{Throttling / Human-in-the-loop}$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Audit Invariant**\n",
        "$$H_t \\neq H_{t-1} \\Rightarrow \\exists\\; \\text{serialized control event}$$"
      ]
    },
